=F0=9F=92=A1 Concept

A digital pet that lives on your phone and *feels your physical world*
through sensor data. It reacts to your real life =E2=80=94 your steps, your=
 sleep
patterns, your rushed mornings, your lazy Sundays. It grows a personality
over time, and shares its perspective on your life through Instagram-style
posts in its own voice.

*Core hook:* Not a wellness app. Not a Tamagotchi. A *character that roasts
your life* using real data =E2=80=94 and people can follow it.
